metadata.description:
**Cult of dog is a web3 drop studio. We use web3 tech to create products, experiences and memes that influence the public conversation. All drops generate profit, no yield farm funny business here.**

Web3 laced with technical jargon that turns off most people. Cult of Dog is creating memes that speak the language of popular culture while making a profit. We use these popular themes to trojan horse web3 tech and ideals into the mainstream.

Cult of Dog token holders help govern what drops get funded and how to use the treasury.
metadata.name: The Cult of Dog Devotee #1
